{"title":"[測試]Jest install","date":"2020-06-17T08:40:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 17, 2020","L":"06/17/2020","MM-DD":"06-17"},"link":"2020/06/17/jestInstall","tags":["Jest","unitTest"],"updated":"2020-06-19T16:14:26.079Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"jest\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/17/jestInstall#jest\"></a>jest</h1>\n<h2 id=\"安裝流程\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/17/jestInstall#安裝流程\"></a>安裝流程</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>首先第一步必須要在你的電腦安裝node<br>\n(<font color=\"red\">由於安裝node.js己經內建NPM，所以不用再另外安裝</font>)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DPHzTNH.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>建立一個專案資料夾（jestPractice），並進入到資料夾底下進行初始化。<br>\n初始化的過程中會產生一支package.json檔案</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm init</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>利用npm 安裝jest。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// -D:表示的是dependence</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 會把jest 的相依套件連結到 package.json</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    npm install jest@<span class=\"number\">24.8</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span> -D</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>安裝完以後可以看package.json中的 devDependencies使否有增加<br>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IR90yhK.png\" alt></p>\n<p><code>注意</code></p>\n<p>修改package.json檔案內容中的script</p>\n<p><font color=\"blue\">如果想要用npm跑jest， script要修改</font></p>\n<p>指令：<code>npm test</code> 等同於 <code>npm jest</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">\"scripts\"</span>: {</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">\"test\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"jest\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">\"coverage\"</span>:<span class=\"string\">\"jest --coverage\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">},</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>如果不想要修改script的話可以在終端機使用<font color=\"red\">npx</font>的方式，例如：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx jest --coverage</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>生成環境建制(產生jest.config)</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx jest --init</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"jest-常見的指令\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/17/jestInstall#jest-常見的指令\"></a>jest 常見的指令</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>幫<font color=\"red\">所有</font>的檔案進行測試</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx jest</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>幫<font color=\"red\">想要</font>的檔案進行測試</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx jest apple.test.js</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>幫測試檔案生成<font color=\"red\">覆蓋率報表</font></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx jest --coverage</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"jest引入ES6的語法\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/06/17/jestInstall#jest引入ES6的語法\"></a>jest引入ES6的語法</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>安裝babel的相關檔案</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install @babel/core@<span class=\"number\">7.4</span><span class=\"number\">.5</span> @babel/preset-env@<span class=\"number\">7.4</span><span class=\"number\">.5</span> --D</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>在根目錄下新增一個檔案（.babelrc），並且修改檔案內容</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"presets\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        [</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"string\">\"@babel/preset-env\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            {</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"string\">\"targets\"</span>: {</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"string\">\"node\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"current\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                }</span><br><span class=\"line\">            }</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p>這樣依來ES6的語法就可以使用了<br>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ub6Or5p.png\" alt><br>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/atXcoFy.png\" alt></p>\n<p>資料來源:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://jestjs.io/docs/zh-Hans/configuration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">jest官網</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2019/02/npx.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">npx的使用方式</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>","next":{"title":"[正則表達式](一) ","link":"2020/03/22/RegExp-1"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/06/17/jestInstall/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"jest","index":"1","children":[{"title":"","id":"安裝流程","index":"1.1"},{"title":"","id":"jest-常見的指令","index":"1.2"},{"title":"","id":"jest引入ES6的語法","index":"1.3"}]}]}